ADR-05 — Expose a RESTful API for Core Complaint Operations
Status: Accepted
Context
The CMS may be extended with mobile apps, chatbots, or partner integrations.
Decision
Use Django REST Framework to expose RESTful JSON API endpoints.
Rationale
•	Industry standard for distributed systems.
•	DRF provides authentication classes, permission classes, serialisers, throttling.
•	Supports stateless communication and scaling.
Consequences
Positive: High interoperability and consistent API design.
Negative: Requires versioning strategy for future evolution.
